    <item>
      <title>塔塔钢铁报告称，由于价格下跌，利润暴跌 64%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/tata-steel-reports-64-decline-in-fourth-quarter-profit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度领先的合金生产商之一塔塔钢铁有限公司 (Tata Steel Ltd.) 报告称，受价格下跌和一次性损失的拖累，该公司第四季度利润较上年同期下降了 64%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/tata-steel-reports-64-decline-in-fourth-quarter-profit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 13:30:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
